name: Just Tap To Cheer - All Stars Cheerleader Running Dance Competition
name_original: Just Tap To Cheer - All Stars Cheerleader Running Dance Competition
description:
————Once again the cheerleader is back to entertain you all—————

It’s time to turn your vibes and stay on with the cheerleader as she going to perform some jumping acts in the mid of the field applaused by thousands of her fans. She is crazy and moves on dancing, jumping, running and so on and on in this endless game.

Enjoy the competition while avoiding avoiding other cheerleader and obstacles as well

Gameplay

• Tap to jump
• Hold longer to jump higher

Have crazy fun with this pretty lady
